    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine with only minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing light wear on the driver's seat bolster but no rips or stains. Mechanically, the car is solid, shifts smoothly, and has a complete service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair overall condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a small tear in the driver's seat, though all basic electronics and the air conditioning are still operational. It is a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This unit exhibits a level of care that borders on the fastidious, presenting in a condition that mirrors its original delivery state. With flawless aesthetics and mechanical integrity beyond reproach, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking an uncompromising driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it's looking absolutely flawless inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that 'new car' feel. If you're looking for something that's been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade example of the E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This unit has been meticulously maintained, with a documented rod bearing service and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement already completed. The double VANOS system operates with surgical precision, delivering linear power through the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec McPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup, devoid of any bushing deflection. Finished in original factory paint with zero oxidation, the exterior is complemented by pristine Style 67 forged wheels. This is a turn-key enthusiast investment with optimal compression across all cylinders and a bone-dry undercarriage.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No scratches or mechanical defects. Original paint. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from even the smallest stone chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in an absolute pristine state; the premium leather seats show zero signs of bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains intact. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. With exceptionally low mileage and a history of careful, adult-only ownership, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly 'as-new' example. The sale includes both original keys, all owner's manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
